<h1>Upgraded Ramen Recipe Ingredients : </h1>
<ul>
<li>Miso Paste</li>
<li>Vegetables</li>
<li>Soft Boiled Egg</li>
<li>Sesame Seeds</li>
</ul>

<h1>Upgraded Ramen Step by Step:</h1>
<ol>
<li>Cook your instant ramen. </li>
<li>Make the sauce</li>
<li>Toss. Add the drained noodles to the pan, turn up the heat, and toss to coat.</li>
<li>Cook the egg.</li>
<li>Serve. Place the noodles in a bowl and finish with sliced scallions and everything bagel spice. Enjoy hot!</li>
</ol>
